Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.84,0:10:25.32,List5,,512,0,182,,Jaehime
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.32,0:10:27.14,List6,,0,120,200,,Zenda
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.32,0:10:27.14,List6,,466,0,196,,Miruku
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.92,0:10:28.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Moje taky.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.60,0:10:30.62,List7,,0,200,276,,Makabe
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.60,0:10:30.62,List7,,300,0,303,,Makoto
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.06,0:10:32.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Och, tenhle člověk.
